  <brief_title>Low-dose Spinal Morphine for Post-Thoracotomy Pain After Video-Assisted Thoracoscopic Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Low-dose Spinal Morphine for Post-Thoracotomy Pain After Video-Assisted Thoracoscopic Surgery: A Prospective Randomized Double-Blind Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
